  "instructions": [
    "Heat the peanut oil in a large skillet or wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the carrots and cook for an additional 4-5 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Add the peanuts and cook for 1-2 minutes, or until fragrant.",
    "Add the Thai red curry paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let cook for 2-3 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened.",
    "Stir in the lime juice and soy sauce.",
    "Season with sugar to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or noodles."
